    <svcproc svcproctype="describe" graphiccount="0">
        <title>Event Logging System</title>
        <para>The event logging system records engine operation above maximum rpm (overspeed), high coolant temperature,
            low coolant level, or low oil pressure. The readings for the odometer and hourmeter are stored in the ECM
            memory at the time of an event and can be retrieved using the EST.
        </para>
    </svcproc>
